Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.55,0:22:50.51,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)}{\blur3}Cut the Rope
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.51,0:22:52.10,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}旋轉大腦的數值
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.51,0:22:52.10,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}頭をめぐる數值は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.10,0:22:54.22,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,250)}{\blur3}繪出螺旋急速上升
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.10,0:22:54.22,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,250)}{\blur3}螺旋を描き急上昇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.22,0:22:57.77,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}沒注意到巨大的過失
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.22,0:22:57.77,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}重大な過ちにも氣づかずに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.77,0:23:01.23,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}人與人之間相互連接
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.77,0:23:01.23,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}人から人へとつながる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.23,0:23:04.86,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}閃耀著淡淡青藍色的Wire
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.23,0:23:04.86,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}淡く青藍に輝くWire
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.86,0:23:08.82,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}美麗異常 彷如絲綢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.86,0:23:08.82,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}とてもきれいでまるで絹の糸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.82,0:23:12.87,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這就是被稱作命運的鎖鏈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.82,0:23:12.87,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}これが運命という鎖なのか
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.87,0:23:16.33,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}尋找著 但糾纏著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.87,0:23:16.33,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}探して でも 絡まって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.33,0:23:18.08,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}無法到達
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.33,0:23:18.08,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}だどり著けない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.08,0:23:20.29,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}What is Wired Life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.08,0:23:20.29,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}What is Wired Life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.50,0:23:23.84,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}無法逃避之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.50,0:23:23.84,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}逃れられないなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.84,0:23:26.01,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}愚蠢卻又美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.84,0:23:26.01,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}愚かで美しい
