Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.22,0:23:33.14,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}無法到達
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.22,0:23:33.14,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}だどり著けない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.14,0:23:35.35,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}What is Wired Life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.14,0:23:35.35,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}What is Wired Life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.35,0:23:38.68,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}無法逃避之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.35,0:23:38.68,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}逃れられないなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.68,0:23:41.10,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}愚蠢卻又美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.68,0:23:41.10,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}愚かで美しい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:45.02,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}{\blur3}There is Wired Life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:45.02,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}{\blur3}There is Wired Life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.41,0:23:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 奧村同學他突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.25,0:23:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說過「要是敢傷害我的同伴 我一定絕不留情殺掉你」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.01,0:24:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了嗎 再次暴走的話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.39,0:24:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥就…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.79,0:24:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,子貓丸！！
